I sorta do.

42:02.896 --> 42:04.163
Hey, Ted.

42:04.197 --> 42:05.164
Yeah.

42:05.198 --> 42:07.233
Exactly where are
the oranges?

42:07.266 --> 42:10.169
Oh, they're out of season
in this part of California

42:10.203 --> 42:11.871
