42:20.714 --> 42:21.648
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

42:21.681 --> 42:22.916
Whoa, whoa!

42:22.949 --> 42:24.851
Whoa, whoa!
This is not forward!

42:24.884 --> 42:29.756
That's not forward!
This is not forward!

42:29.789 --> 42:32.258
